headline: Millrose Properties: The new kid on the REIT block
summary: Millrose Properties (MRP) was spun off from Lennar (LEN) in February of 2025 and just reported its first quarterly results. Millrose Properties CEO and president Darren Richman joins Market Domination Overtime to discuss the company's business, the state of housing, who the company's customers are, and where they are seeing opportunities. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.

headline: 3 Reasons LEN is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Lennar’s stock price has taken a beating over the past six months, shedding 34.4% of its value and falling to $110.77 per share. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
